General.Name: Fodelia
General.Description: Fodelia Oyj operates as a food company in Finland. The company offers crispy potato chips and additive-free corn snacks to retail stores and central wholesale businesses, as well as importers and retail stores in export target countries. It also provides Feelia, a pre-cooked meal for various clients, including municipalities, care companies, lunch restaurants, central wholesale businesses, wholesalers, and households. The company was founded in 1979 and is based in Pyhäntä, Finland.
